# Global Components & Animations

All persistent elements and animation specifications. These components exist across ALL sections.

---

## FLOATING MARIGOLD PETALS (Ambient Layer)

Persistent layer across all sections. Like walking through a decorated palace corridor.

| Property | Value | Count | 8-12 petals visible at any time |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Colors | `#D4A017` and `#C9A96E` at 25-35% opacity | Size | 8-15px each, varied for depth |
| Animation | CSS-only keyframes: downward drift + horizontal sway (sine wave). Random duration 8-15s per petal | Layer | z-index 1, behind all content |
| Performance | Pure CSS, GPU-accelerated transform: translate3d(). Max 12 DOM elements | Accessibility | prefers-reduced-motion: hide entirely |
| Mobile | 5-6 petals on screens under 480px | Interaction | pointer-events: none -- never blocks taps |

