## DIYA (LAMP) LIGHTING MICRO-ANIMATION

Every section heading gets a tiny diya that lights up on section enter.

| Property | Value | Icon | 24px diya SVG, positioned left of heading |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Idle State | Static gold outline, no flame, `#8B7340` at 40% | On Enter | Flame appears (SVG/CSS), gold glow pulse radiates outward |
| Glow | Radial gradient `#C9A96E` to transparent, 0 to 30px radius, fades 0.6s | After | Stays lit with static flame as gold accent |
| Duration | 0.5s flame + 0.6s glow | Sections | All headings except Section 0 (Ganesha has own opening) |

