## GOLD SHIMMER TEXT EFFECT

Matte antique gold light sweep. Applied to couple names and section headings.

| Property | Value | Technique | CSS background-clip: text with animated linear gradient |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Gradient | `#8B7340` -> `#C9A96E` -> `#D4B87A` -> `#C9A96E` -> `#8B7340` | Background Size | 200% 100% |
| Couple Names | 4s per sweep loop | Section Headings | 6s per sweep loop (subtler) |
| Fallback | Static `#C9A96E` for unsupported browsers | Key Rule | MATTE only. No sparkle, no glitter, no bright flashes. Gentle light shift across gold surface |

