## JAALI TEXTURE GUIDELINES

- Use as background overlays ONLY, never foreground
- Opacity: 5-10% max over midnight blue
- Patterns: Rajasthani jaali cutwork, arch silhouettes, paisley borders
- Position: Edges and corners, never center-blocking content
- SVG format, gold-tinted `#C9A96E` at 8% opacity
- Max file size: 15KB per SVG